#: ../../A/adger.rst:9
msgid ""
"[UCLA mutant of :ref:`nadger`\\, poss. also from the middle name of an "
"infamous :ref:`tenured-graduate-student`\\] To make a bonehead move with "
"consequences that could have been foreseen with even slight mental effort. "
"E.g., \"He started removing files and promptly adgered the whole project\". "
"Compare :ref:`dumbass-attack`\\."
msgstr ""
"[\\ :ref:`nadger`\\ のUCLAでの変異形。おそらく悪名高いある\\ :ref:`tenured-graduate-"
"student`\\ "
"のミドルネームにも由来]ほんの少し頭を使えば予見できたはずの結果を伴う、ばかげた手を打つこと。例:「彼はファイルを削除し始めて、たちまちプロジェクト全体をadgerした(台無しにした)」。\\"
" :ref:`dumbass-attack`\\ と比較せよ。"
